{"tid":1827792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（輸出革命）高雄驚現「光復高雄」揮春、貼紙","createTime":"2020-01-17T08:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T15:31:22.000Z","uid":258731,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de98b68acfa4878f3ddefedb0d729a505215a459","tid":1827792,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXxRAg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXxRAg1.jpg&h=def72be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(罷韓熱潮）光復高雄「春聯」太夯 1200份25分鐘被搶光<br />\n<br />\n〔記者王榮祥／高雄報導〕台灣基進今下午在凹子底民主市集發放光復高雄「春聯」，繼光復高雄貼紙後又勾起排隊人潮，1200份春聯不到25分鐘就被領光，也為晚上的高雄總造勢成功暖場。<br />\n<br />\n台灣基進今晚將在高雄凹子底公園舉辦「堅定無畏，衝進國會」高雄總造勢，下午在同個場地先規劃民主市集活動，吸引不少民眾參與。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wVcjMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wVcjMD.jpg&h=fa5fd8ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基進指出，活動開始不久，現場即出現欲索取光復高雄春聯的人龍，不到25分鐘、1200份光復高雄春聯就被橫掃一空。<br />\n<br />\n張博洋酸，韓國瑜的「庶民經濟」早已破功，芭樂政見還沒實現就已被「罷韓經濟」取代，只要是罷韓活動的現場，都能明顯看見周遭攤販的買氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VVrUsDnle90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVVrUsDnle90&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=c80b6829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VVrUsDnle90</a><br />\n里長莊晉勳則說，會自製春聯發放，是期許「新年新高雄、高雄新希望」，要把過去屬於高雄人的光榮與驕傲重新找回來，希望罷韓熱度繼續發燒，在今年成功罷免韓國瑜達成雙殺目標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QK3tCxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQK3tCxN.jpg&h=9a53780f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民眾排隊等著領取光復高雄春聯。（記者王榮祥翻攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3030669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3030669&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=fefe1dc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3030669&h=e828d86f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3030669</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S2U4Vkv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2U4Vkv.jpg&h=55996619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNimc7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNimc7p.jpg&h=5f3ab682&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70c4b62de31bcc2c86b779b3cd5d1388e299ada4","tid":1827792,"uid":258731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"香港都要努力光復<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f54e7f207ad2d796d76797b9442b5ee977b6f8f","tid":1827792,"uid":271516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images1.epochhk.com/pictures/123304/2019-09-01_224417@1200x1200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages1.epochhk.com%2Fpictures%2F123304%2F2019-09-01_224417%401200x1200.jpg&h=c4a53179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2f45b4c67ac83b1b260155b6318b9617acf3c33","tid":1827792,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bc05b3231aaa6a2eaaf8ba10c99d480392d1406","tid":1827792,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"19f19939f74d5e85426734113da6f8b6102ec041","tid":1827792,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"台灣妹老左就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"